\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 30th. \_ This was our last day in the Egyptian wilderness. We entered on a much more mountainou
s region. The heat very great; we literally panted for a breath of wind. The Bedouins begged handkerchiefs to cover their heads, and often cast themselves under a bush for shade. Towards sunset we came down on the old ruins of Rhinoculura, now buried in t
he sand; and soon after our camels kneeled down at the gates of E1 Arish, the last town of the Egyptian frontier.
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 31st. \_ We spent in El Arish, being unable to get fresh camels. We bought a sheep for 5s.\_drank freely of their delightful water; what a bless
ing after the desert}{\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 ! F}{\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 ound out the river of Egypt, the boundary of Judah mentioned in the Bible, quite dry.
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\i\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 E1Arish, }{\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 lst June.\_Visited the school\_a curiosity. All the children sit cross\_
legged on the floor, rocking to and fro, repeating something in Arabic. We had a curious interview with the Governor, sitting in the gate in the ancient manner. We are quite expert now at taking off our shoes and sitting in the Eastern mode. \_ Smok}{
\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 ing, }{\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 and coffee in very small cups, are the constant accompaniments of these
 visits. Left the same evening, and did not reach Sheikh Juidhe, in the land of the Philistines, till the sun was just bursting into view.
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 
